---
import Base from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---
<Base title="Modern Slavery Statement"><Fragment slot="header"><Header /></Fragment>

  <section class="pt-28 pb-16 bg-grid" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#eef2ff 0%,#ffffff 35%,#faf5ff 100%)">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="max-w-2xl"><p class="sl">Legal</p><h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-heading font-bold text-gray-900 leading-tight mb-4">Modern slavery statement</h1><p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Published 20 June 2026</p></div></div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 border-t border-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="prose space-y-6">
        <div><h2>1. Introduction</h2><p>Published pursuant to Section 54 of the Modern Slavery Act 2015. Protomon Labs is a computational genomics group operating solely in the UK with a supply chain limited to software services and cloud infrastructure.</p></div>
        <div><h2>2. Policies</h2><p>Ethical Procurement Policy, Code of Conduct, and Whistleblowing Policy. All members are trained on the Modern Slavery Act.</p></div>
        <div><h2>3. Due Diligence</h2><p>We engage with UK- and EEA-based suppliers. Cloud providers' modern slavery statements are reviewed annually.</p></div>
        <div><h2>4. Risk Assessment</h2><p>Risk of modern slavery is very low. We review this assessment annually.</p></div>
        <div><h2>5. Approval</h2><p>This statement was approved by Protomon Labs leadership and will be reviewed annually.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

<Fragment slot="footer"><Footer /></Fragment></Base>